data.eml:eml: Ingolfiella rocaensis sp. nov. (Crustacea: Amphipoda: Ingolfiellidea): first record of ingolfiellidean amphipods in Brazilian waters

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Senna, André R., Serejo, Cristiana S. (2005): Ingolfiella rocaensis sp. nov. (Crustacea: Amphipoda: Ingolfiellidea): first record of ingolfiellidean amphipods in Brazilian waters. Zootaxa 962: 1-6, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.171248
